      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPEAK THE TRUTH (6) is in full flight at present and made it back-to-back wins at this circuit and distance when he came from this barrier and worked to the front before scoring by 2.2m a fortnight ago. Beat all of these rivals there so only needs to hold his form to land the hat trick. TIMS A TROOPER (5) came from wider when runner-up to SPEAK THE TRUTH two back before a brave win here last week, racing up to four wide early before settling in the death seat and toughing it out by 3m. Expect another strong showing. HOT AND TREACHEROUS NZ (1) hinted at a return to form when a close second from a 30m handicap last start and he gets the aid of the inside barrier. A good draw could see HECTOR NZ (3) add to his recent string of top-four finishes.",
